          Resource which represents a single file, and is used to download the file content.
 class FileListResource
          The filelist resource represents a list of files using XML.
 class LoginResource
          The login resource performs authentication using GoogleDocs's class and on failure redirects again to Google's authentication page, and on success redirects to the filelisting for all devices at URL "/all/html/filelist".
 class SettingsResource
          The SettingsResource is used to get and set the settings of the user's root directory.
 class UploadResource
          Resource which represents a single file, and is used to upload the file to user's GoogleDocs account.
